---
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const metadata = {
  title: 'About Me – John Doe',
  description: 'About John Doe: Digital Retail, E-Commerce, Front-End Web Development.',
  robots: {
    index: false,
    follow: false,
  },
};
---

<PageLayout metadata={metadata}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6 text-center">About Me</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-blue dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-lg">
      <p>Dear Hiring Managers,</p>
      <p>
        If your company values analytical thinking, empathy, and a results-driven mindset, then I believe I can be an
        excellent addition to your team. I am a passionate Retail and E-Commerce Professional with extensive experience
        in managing both physical store operations and digital commerce environments.
      </p>
      <p>
        With over ten years of experience as a Retail Store Manager and E-Commerce Specialist, I have developed a
        holistic approach that connects traditional retail management with modern online strategies to create consistent
        and engaging customer experiences.
      </p>
      <p>
        In my previous roles, I have overseen complete store operations, including purchasing, supplier relations,
        warehouse logistics, and customer service, supported by ERP, CRM, and PIM systems. My back-office expertise
        covers both the passive and active cycles—from stock and invoice management to promotions, returns, and customer
        loyalty programs. At the same time, I bring strong front-office skills in merchandising, visual presentation,
        and multilingual communication (English, German, Italian).
      </p>
      <p>
        Beyond retail, I have hands-on experience in E-Commerce setup and management, having built and optimized online
        stores on various CMS platforms (Shopify, WordPress WooCommerce, PrestaShop, Shopware, Magento, etc.). I
        specialize in UX/UI design, SEO, content creation, and system integration between ERP and web platforms to
        ensure efficient workflows and accurate product data synchronization.
      </p>
      <p>
        My technical background as a Front-End Web Developer (React, Next.js, Vue, Astro) enables me to collaborate
        effectively with developers and marketing teams. Combined with my analytical approach to SEO and web
        performance, I continuously identify opportunities to enhance visibility, user experience, and conversion rates.
      </p>
      <p>
        I am deeply motivated by innovation and process optimization through digitalization, and I bring a proactive,
        collaborative, and customer-centric mindset to every project I join.
      </p>
      <p>
        I would welcome the opportunity to contribute my skills and experience to your company’s growth and would be
        delighted to discuss how I can add value to your team in a personal interview.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you very much for your time and consideration.</p>
      <p>Warm regards,<br />John Doe</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</PageLayout>
